INSERT INTO
    ers_dca_whale_catches (
    message_id,start_timestamp,stop_timestamp,message_version,whale_grenade_number,whale_blubber_measure_a,whale_blubber_measure_b,whale_blubber_measure_c,whale_circumference,whale_fetus_length,whale_gender_id,whale_individual_number,whale_length
   )
SELECT
    *
FROM
    UNNEST(
        $1::BIGINT[],$2::TIMESTAMPTZ[],$3::TIMESTAMPTZ[],$4::INT[],$5::TEXT[],$6::INT[],$7::INT[],$8::INT[],$9::INT[],$10::INT[],$11::INT[],$12::INT[],$13::INT[]
    )
        ON CONFLICT (message_id,start_timestamp,stop_timestamp,whale_grenade_number) DO NOTHING
